    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a mechanically robust example of the celebrated S65-powered platform. The 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 remains the centerpiece, delivering linear power delivery to an 8,400 RPM redline via eight individual throttle bodies. This specimen features the desirable 6-speed manual transmission and the M Variable Differential Lock for optimal torque distribution. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service, ensuring the high-pressure VANOS system operates flawlessly. The chassis retains its precision, benefiting from the weight-saving carbon fiber roof and a well-sorted EDC suspension. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain and subframe remain in excellent functional order, making this a driver-focused machine ready for the canyon or the circuit.",
      "price": 36500.0,
