    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained luxury sedan offers the perfect balance of performance and everyday comfort. The Deep Sea Blue Metallic exterior retains a brilliant, deep shine, though a few minor stone chips on the front bumper reflect its honest road history and daily use. Inside, the smoke-free cabin features supple Oyster leather upholstery that has been regularly conditioned; you\u2019ll find only light, natural creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster and pristine carpets throughout. Mechanically, this vehicle is in robust health with a documented full service history, including a recent comprehensive inspection, oil change, and a fresh set of premium all-season tires. The turbocharged engine pulls smoothly, and the automatic transmission shifts with crisp precision. All onboard electronics, from the high-resolution navigation system to the multi-zone climate control and heated seats, function exactly as intended. This is a reliable, turn-key vehicle for a buyer who appreciates a car that has been cared for with a detail-oriented eye.",
